            "title": "Foraging dispersion of Ryukyu flying-foxes and relationships with fig abundance in East-Asian subtropical island forests",
            "creators": [
                {
                    "creatorType": "author",
                    "firstName": "Ya-Fu",
                    "lastName": "Lee"
                },
                {
                    "creatorType": "author",
